data.description: Nestled in the picturesque Lake Las Vegas area. Former model home, w/over $400,000 in upgrades! Hand-selected designer finishes. Boasting an impressive 3133 sq ft, spacious 4 bed, 4.5-bath the ultimate in comfort & style. Maple flat cabinets, exquisite granite countertops, upgraded appliances. Featuring a wine cooler in the bar area w/sink. Breathtaking 25-ft quartz wall w/fireplace. Sonos sound system both indoors & outdoors with 6 exterior security cameras. Beautiful pool/spa combo, surrounded by plush landscape & enchanting lighting. Extended driveway, epoxy floor in both garages, Garages have Built-In custom cabinets and upgraded storage shelves. Upgraded landscape front/rear, Upgraded pool decking and stamped concrete under patio. Breathtaking views of majestic mountains & dazzling city lights. Don't miss out on the opportunity for this Lake Las Vegas gem. Contact us today to schedule a private showing & discover the lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
